<section xml:id="intro" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
    <title>Introduction</title>
    <p>The main purpose of these notes is to create a template for my future notes. You will find that 
        I have not spent time on the actual content, rather on the structure and formatting. I am new to PreText 
        and I would like to point out that it offers a plathora of  
        <url href="https://pretextbook.org/doc/guide/html/topic-accessibility.html">accessiblity features</url>  that I have not yet explored. 
        I will update these notes as I learn more about PreText and its capabilities.
    </p>
    
</section>
